      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-sqa-mrl2",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 used under a validated SQA plan conforming to ASME V&V 10-2006 and FDA guidance. Version control, regression testing, and release documentation verified. Software qualification records on file confirm Gradation 2 requirements met for MRL 2."
