      "rationale": "At MRL 2, separate numerical solver error assessment beyond code verification is not required per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Iterative convergence monitored via residual drop of 6 orders of magnitude and QoI stabilization; no solver error contributions identified. Scoped out as acceptable for MRL 2 Class II device assessment."
    },
    {
