      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-use-error-scopedout",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal use error assessment is not required per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Simulation setup reviewed by independent analyst; mesh generation, boundary condition assignment, and post-processing scripts version-controlled. Scoped out as acceptable for MRL 2 Class II device assessment."
    },
    {
