      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/morrison-model-form-scopedout",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model form uncertainty quantification beyond validation comparison is not required per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood pump applications. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model is industry-standard for this device class. Scoped out as acceptable for MRL 2."
